(29553, 'Vividol hair oil 120 ml', 'فيفيدول زيت شعر 120 مل', '140', '170', 'Amygadalus+helicanthus+rucula+olea gallica+balm mint+citrus medica+triticum sativum', 'Macro group pharmaceuticals', 'Hair oil', 'زيت شعر', 'علاج تساقط الشعر', 'Hair care', '120 ml', '*an exclusive blend contains amino acids anti-oxidants vitamins & minerals that are derived from the botanical world to revitalize hair & scalp *re-constructs damaged hair by bonding to the weak sites *absorbed quickly non-greasy & contains no animal fats', '6224010643017', '', 4901, '2025-08-15', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(12299, 'Vigorama 50mg 4 f.c.tab.', 'فيجوراما 50 مجم 4اقراص', '', '19', 'Sildenafil', 'Mup', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مقوي للرجال.', 'Tonic for men', '50mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
(1) the treatment of erectile dysfunction [A175582, L5611, F3853, F3856, F3886]; and
(2) treatment of pulmonary hypertension, where:
a) the US FDA specifically indicates sildenafil for the treatment of pulmonary arterial hypertension (PAH) (WHO Group I) in adults to improve exercise ability and delay clinical worsening [F3850]. The delay in clinical worsening was demonstrated when sildenafil was added to background epoprostenol therapy [F3850]. Studies establishing effectiveness were short-term (12 to 16 weeks), and included predominately patients with New York Heart Association (NYHA) Functional Class II-III symptoms and idiopathic etiology (71%) or associated with connective tissue disease (CTD) (25%) [F3850];
